This paper is about salient object detection in videos using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on the use of non-local neural networks, which are a type of deep learning model that has been gaining popularity in recent years. Therefore, it is likely that this paper would also fall under the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural networks (cs.NE).
